00:01:47.140 --> 00:01:51.960
Her size is actually very similar to my Lati Yellow girls: Ichigo and Mocha.

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:54.580
Let me show you both next to each other.

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:06.360
I think little Melo will fit in my doll family perfectly.

00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:09.860
Especially since she can wear the same clothes as Ichigo and Mocha.

00:02:10.480 --> 00:02:12.680
I hope to find time to customize her soon.

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:17.460
And I will definitely share my progress photos on my Instagram and Facebook page.

00:02:18.020 --> 00:02:19.540
Also, before I go:

00:02:19.540 --> 00:02:21.700
I just launched my Patreon page—

00:02:21.700 --> 00:02:26.740
