00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:28.040
So for example:

00:02:28.040 --> 00:02:30.900
If you want to see my next week's Untangled episode,

00:02:30.900 --> 00:02:34.980
you can see it straight away right now by becoming my Patreon—

00:02:34.980 --> 00:02:39.360
instead of waiting another week or two before it becomes public on YouTube.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:41.720
Thank you so much for watching!

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:44.220
If this is your first time on my channel,

00:02:44.220 --> 00:02:50.120
then I would love to have you subscribed so you don't miss out on any future videos, giveaways, and other events.

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:54.800
If you enjoyed this video, give it a thumbs up, comment, and share.

00:02:54.800 --> 00:03:00.200
That way, I know which videos you enjoy and I will make sure that I make more of them.

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:02.940
Have a great day, and I will see you in the next one.

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:04.020
Bye! :)

